{"url":"http://amyzzung.tistory.com/m/post/424","title":"자꾸 땡기는 감칠맛이 있는 '알리오올리오파스타 만드는 법'","category":"면요리","date":"2014/10/31 08:00","ingredient":"마늘,파스타,파슬리,식용유,건고추,홍고추,허브,스파게티면,올리브오일,크림,스파게티 면,멸치액젓,참치,후추,세이지,파마산치즈가루,오일,통마늘,삼겹살,파마산 치즈가루,토마토","text":"<div class=\"area_content useless_p_margin\"> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">담백하면서 재료 맛이 살아 있는 오일파스타를 좋아하는데요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">그중에 마늘</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">오일</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">파스타라는 알리오(마늘)</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">올리오(오일)</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">파스타를 사먹곤합니다.</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">그런데 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">크림이나 토마토 소스도 아닌 고작 마늘과 오일만 있는 </span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">이 단순한 파스타를&nbsp;&nbsp;삼겹살보다 비싸게</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;주고 사먹기 아깝다는 생각이 들데요.</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">이탈리아 요리를 할 줄 아는 지인의 도움을 받아</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">의외의 재료 멸치액젓, 매운 홍고추, 파마산치즈가루를 넣어</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">감칠맛 제대로 나게 '알리오올리오 파스타'를 만들어 봤습니다.</span></p> \n <div class=\"ad_t2\" style=\"MARGIN: 17px 0px 17px -2px\" align=\"center\"> \n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://cfs.tistory.com/custom/blog/154/1542025/skin/images/AdsenseM_Top.js\"></script> \n </div> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile24.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F26346C3854511CFB0F21AD\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p><strong></strong>&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; COLOR: #f261df\">자꾸</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; COLOR: #008299\">땡기는</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; COLOR: #ff5e00\">감칠맛이</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; COLOR: #47c83e\">있는 </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffc19e\">'알리오올리오</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffc19e\">파스타 만드는 법'</span></span></strong></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMIL