pan><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">특유 풍미~가 느껴져요.</span></span></p> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;* 멸치액젓이 충격적인가요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">? </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">지인의&nbsp;강력추천으로 넣었는데&nbsp;전혀 비리지 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">않고 감칠맛이 나서 좋아요.</span></span></p> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;* 허브는 파슬리를 주로 사용하나 저는 그냥 집에 있는것 (세이지)사용했습니다.</span></p>\n </blockquote> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; COLOR: #6699ff\">2. 재료 손질</span></strong></span></p> \n <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">(모든 재료의 깨끗한 손질 과정은 필수이므로 생략함)</span></p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">▣ 마늘</span></strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> : 0.5cm 두께로 얇게 저며주세요 (슬라이스)</span></span></p> \n <blockquote class=\"tx-quote-tistory\"> \n  <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;* 두께는 개인 취향에 따라 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;더 두껍거나 더 얇게 썰어주세요.</span></p>\n </blockquote> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">▣ 홍고추 </span></strong><span style=\"FONT