\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;* 면이 서로 달라붙지 않게 식용유를, </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">짭조름하게 양념이 되게</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> 소금을 넣어주세요.</span></span></p> \n  <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;* 촉촉한 파스타를 만들고 싶을때는 면 삶을 물을 몇숟가락 넣어주면 좋으니 삶은 물은 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">버리지마세요.</span></span></p>\n </blockquote> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile9.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F211DCC3854511CFE2D6099\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">▣ 둘째</span></strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> - 면이 삶아 지는 동안&nbsp; 약불에 달구어진 팬에 올리오오일을 두르고 마늘, 매운 홍고추를 넣고 볶아주세요. (마늘이 노릇해질때까지)</span></span></p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2420783854511CFE2925EF\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p>&nbsp;</p> \n <p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">▣ 셋째</span></strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"> - 마늘이 노릇하게 구워졌다면 삶은 면을 넣고 잠시만 볶아주세요.</span></span></p> \n <div style=\"MARGIN: 17px 0px 17px -2px\" align=\"center\"> \n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://cfs.tistory.com/custom/blog/154/1542025/skin/images/AdsenseM_ctr.js\"></script> \n 